column4: Living in a couple: Married or in a registered same-sex civil partnership
column7: Not living in a couple: Single (never married or never registered a same-sex civil partnership)
column8: Not living in a couple: Married or in a registered same-sex civil partnership
column9: Not living in a couple: Separated (but still legally married or still legally in a same-sex civil partnership)
column10: Not living in a couple: Divorced or formerly in a same-sex civil partnership which is now legally dissolved
column11: Not living in a couple: Widowed or surviving partner from a same-sex civil partnership
